[center] [size=18pt][b]Information:[/b][/size][/center]
I will be updating this thread mostly daily to check on the current status of A to F. I will also spend my time checking it if the link works and if people are being rude. My cousin Carlos, spend the time coding this with my cousin Hector so please don't abuse this and say it is completely your because it really isn't. My Cousin Carlos said i can release this because he ISN'T COMPLETELY FINISHED but it doesn't have all the Cache Packed in 742. He also told me to give him credits and his brother: Hector if your going to use this. Thanks and i hope you people find this useful as usual this isn't the final cache he isn't done he said the next cache will take at least 2 days if not 3 days, so this is more of a pre-beta cache he forgot to add some content i don't understand because it is JAGEX Talk. Again thanks for clicking the thread, it means a lot.
[size=18pt]I GIVE PERMISSION TO RELEASE ON ANY OTHER WEBSITE: GIVE ME AND MY COUSINS CREDIT[/size]
[center][size=18pt][b]Cache Information:[/b][/size][/center]
[ul][li][742] Maps. Including: New Al-Kharid.[/li] [li][742] Sounds + Music. All around the World.[/li] [li][742] Weapons + Armour. Including: New Looks.[/li] [li][742] Gfx + Animations. All like 742.[/li] [li][742] Emotes. Including: All mostly working.[/li] [li][742] Squeal of Fortune.[/li] [li][742] Grand Exchange Maps.[/li] [li][742] Grand Exchange Interfaces.[/li] [li][742] Grand Exchange Booth.[/li] [li][742] Achievement Sets.[/li] [li][742] Npcs Including: Mr Ex, and really awesome.[/li] [li][742] Character. Including: Awesome Make-Over Mage[/li] [li][742] Shop Interfaces. All like 742.[/li] [li][742] Manual Set Up, screen.[/li] [li][742] Full-screen Works.[/li] [li][742] Resizeable Works.[/li] [li][742] Tabarea + Chatarea.[/li] [li][742] Nex + Nex Maps.[/li] [li][742] Godwars Dungeon.[/li] [li][742] Godwars Npcs.[/li] [li][742] Queen Black Dragon[/li] [li][742] Queen Black Dragon Maps[/li] [li][742] World Maps works, takes 6 Seconds to load.[/li] [li][742] Bank + Bank Tab Interfaces[/li] [li]AND WAY MORE [742]!![/li][/ul]
[center][size=18pt][b]MEDIA:[/b][/size][/center]
World Map: [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/2eaqm9v.jpg[/img]

*Note all these pictures are from my development thread, i didn't feel like more images.
[center] [size=18pt][b]Requirements:[/b][/size][/center]
Your [Matrix, zenith, pvp, rune-evo, nr v1,v2,v3,v4, etc.] Source must also have cache in their source if not your Source isn't workable. This might work for the following revisions: 718, 667, 735, 742, 745, 721, 724.
